---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Teaching - John [Last Name]" description="Teaching philosophy and experience of John [Last Name]">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
    <!-- Header -->
    <div class="mb-12 text-center">
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-primary-400 mb-4">
        Teaching
      </h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-neutral-300 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        Empowering learners through technology, coding, and creative problem-solving.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Philosophy Placeholder -->
    <div class="bg-neutral-800 rounded-lg p-8 border border-neutral-700 shadow-lg mb-8">
      <div class="flex items-center mb-6">
        <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-secondary-400 mr-3" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 6.253v13m0-13C10.832 5.477 9.246 5 7.5 5S4.168 5.477 3 6.253v13C4.168 18.477 5.754 18 7.5 18s3.332.477 4.5 1.253m0-13C13.168 5.477 14.754 5 16.5 5c1.747 0 3.332.477 4.5 1.253v13C19.832 18.477 18.247 18 16.5 18c-1.746 0-3.332.477-4.5 1.253"></path>
        </svg>
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-primary-400">Teaching Philosophy</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-neutral-900 rounded-lg p-6 border border-neutral-700">
        <p class="text-neutral-300 italic text-center">
          Content coming soon - this section will feature my teaching philosophy and approach to education.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Experience Areas -->
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-8">
      <div class="bg-neutral-800 rounded-lg p-6 border border-neutral-700">
        <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
          <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-primary-500 mr-3" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M10 20l4-16m4 4l4 4-4 4M6 16l-4-4 4-4"></path>
          </svg>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary-400">Coding Education</h3>
        </div>
        <p class="text-neutral-300 leading-relaxed">
          Teaching programming fundamentals through engaging, hands-on projects that make abstract
          concepts tangible and fun for students of all ages.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-neutral-800 rounded-lg p-6 border border-neutral-700">
        <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
          <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-secondary-500 mr-3" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 3v2m6-2v2M9 19v2m6-2v2M5 9H3m2 6H3m18-6h-2m2 6h-2M7 19h10a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2zM9 9h6v6H9V9z"></path>
          </svg>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-secondary-400">Robotics</h3>
        </div>
        <p class="text-neutral-300 leading-relaxed">
          Combining hardware and software instruction to help students understand how technology
          works in the physical world through Arduino and robotics projects.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-neutral-800 rounded-lg p-6 border border-neutral-700">
        <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
          <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-primary-500 mr-3" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9.75 17L9 20l-1 1h8l-1-1-.75-3M3 13h18M5 17h14a2 2 0 002-2V5a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z"></path>
          </svg>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary-400">Educational Technology</h3>
        </div>
        <p class="text-neutral-300 leading-relaxed">
          Leveraging technology to create more effective and engaging learning experiences,
          from interactive simulations to educational game design.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-neutral-800 rounded-lg p-6 border border-neutral-700">
        <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
          <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-secondary-500 mr-3" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 15l-2 5L9 9l11 4-5 2zm0 0l5 5M7.188 2.239l.777 2.897M5.136 7.965l-2.898-.777M13.95 4.05l-2.122 2.122m-5.657 5.656l-2.12 2.122"></path>
          </svg>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-secondary-400">Instructional Design</h3>
        </div>
        <p class="text-neutral-300 leading-relaxed">
          Designing curriculum and learning materials that align with educational goals and
          engage diverse learners through evidence-based practices.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Coming Soon Banner -->
    <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-primary-900/20 to-secondary-900/20 rounded-lg p-8 border border-primary-700/30 text-center">
      <svg class="w-16 h-16 text-primary-500 mx-auto mb-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 6.253v13m0-13C10.832 5.477 9.246 5 7.5 5S4.168 5.477 3 6.253v13C4.168 18.477 5.754 18 7.5 18s3.332.477 4.5 1.253m0-13C13.168 5.477 14.754 5 16.5 5c1.747 0 3.332.477 4.5 1.253v13C19.832 18.477 18.247 18 16.5 18c-1.746 0-3.332.477-4.5 1.253"></path>
      </svg>
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-neutral-200 mb-3">More Content Coming Soon</h2>
      <p class="text-neutral-300 max-w-xl mx-auto">
        This page will be expanded with detailed information about teaching experience,
        curriculum samples, student projects, and educational resources.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
